---
import Container from "../shared/Container.astro";
---

<section id="cta" class="pb-20">
  <Container>
    <div
      class="w-full relative py-8 md:py-10 px-6 md:px-8 rounded-2xl bg-gradient-to-tr from-gray-100 to-gray-200 dark:from-gray-900"
    >
      <div class="mx-auto text-center max-w-xl md:max-w-2xl relative">
        <h5
          class="text-3xl/tight sm:text-4xl/tight md:text-5xl/tight
          font-bold text-heading-1"
        >
          Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)
        </h5>

        <ul class="mt-8 space-y-4 text-heading-3 font-medium">
          <li>
            <span
              class="font-bold bg-box-bg rounded-full w-8 h-8 mr-3  inline-flex justify-center items-center"
              >&checkmark;</span
            >Do you sell my property or buy it directly?<br />
            We are not real estate agents. Instead, we buy properties directly. After
            purchasing, we may repair and resell or keep them as rentals.
          </li>

          <li>
            <span
              class="font-bold bg-box-bg rounded-full w-8 h-8 mr-3 inline-flex justify-center items-center"
              >&checkmark;</span
            > Do you offer competitive prices? <br />
            We aim for a fair discount, but our value lies in fast cash offers, quick closings, and no fees or repairs required from sellers.
          </li>

          <li>
            <span
              class="font-bold bg-box-bg rounded-full w-8 h-8 mr-3 inline-flex justify-center items-center"
              >&checkmark;</span
            > Are there fees or commissions?<br />
            No. We cover the closing costs, and there are no commissions when you sell directly to us.
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</section>
